docs {
  # Get Vendor by ID

  Returns a single vendor by its unique identifier.

  ## Path Parameters

  | Param | Description |
  |-------|-------------|
  | id | Vendor identifier (e.g., `nvidia`, `amd`, `google`, `intel`) |

  ## Response Shape

  ```json
  {
    "id": "nvidia",
    "name": "NVIDIA",
    "description": "GPU and AI computing company",
    "website": "https://nvidia.com"
  }
  ```

  ## Error Responses

  - `404 Not Found`: Vendor with given ID does not exist
  - `400 Bad Request`: Invalid resource name
}
